01:31:43.728 --> 01:31:44.596 position:38% line:83% align:start
[GINOZA]
Let's go!

01:31:48.400 --> 01:31:50.435 position:35% line:83% align:start
[KUNIZUKA]
Inspector, are you all right?

01:31:53.471 --> 01:31:55.774 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AKANE]
What are you guys doing here?

01:31:55.807 --> 01:31:58.143 position:24% line:83% align:start
