01:37:42.921 --> 01:37:47.458 position:13% line:83% align:start
[AKANE] You're criminally
asymptomatic. I knew it.

01:37:47.492 --> 01:37:49.928 position:41% line:83% align:start
[HANG]
So, you were aware?

01:37:49.961 --> 01:37:51.230 position:16% line:83% align:start
[AKANE] A little birdie
mentioned something

01:37:51.263 --> 01:37:53.631 position:5% line:89% align:start
about you being a doppelgänger.

01:37:53.665 --> 01:37:55.900 position:21% line:83% align:start
But I bet he didn't
even have a clue.

01:37:57.635 --> 01:37:59.238 position:21% line:83% align:start
[AKANE] The Japanese
ministries and agencies

01:37:59.271 --> 01:38:02.074 position:21% line:83% align:start
are already full of
cyborg impostors.

01:38:02.107 --> 01:38:03.142 position:41% line:83% align:start
[HANG]
True.

01:38:03.175 --> 01:38:07.545 position:19% line:83% align:start
And Colonel Wong just
assumed that I was human.

01:38:07.578 --> 01:38:09.714 position:16% line:83% align:start
A man who had undergone
some plastic surgery

01:38:09.747 --> 01:38:11.783 position:13% line:89% align:start
to look like the Chairman.

01:38:11.816 --> 01:38:14.585 position:27% line:83% align:start
Perhaps in time,
he would've suspected.

01:38:15.586 --> 01:38:18.990 position:21% line:83% align:start
[HANG] After all, it
was only two days ago

01:38:19.023 --> 01:38:21.526 position:24% line:83% align:start
when I met the man
for the first time.

01:38:23.528 --> 01:38:25.563 position:41% line:83% align:start
[HANG]
In fact, truth be told,

01:38:25.596 --> 01:38:28.800 position:19% line:83% align:start
I came to SEAUn on the
same flight as you did.

01:38:30.001 --> 01:38:31.536 position:41% line:83% align:start
[HANG]
It's a logistical nightmare

01:38:31.569 --> 01:38:33.838 position:19% line:83% align:start
rotating cyborgs into
a foreign nation.

01:38:33.871 --> 01:38:35.107 position:30% line:89% align:start
So it's true.

01:38:35.140 --> 01:38:38.042 position:21% line:83% align:start
Just like Inspector
Shimotsuki theorized.

01:38:38.077 --> 01:38:39.711 position:13% line:83% align:start
Everything that's happened
has played out

01:38:39.744 --> 01:38:42.880 position:24% line:83% align:start
exactly according
to your plan.

01:38:42.914 --> 01:38:44.615 position:30% line:89% align:start
Sibyl System.

01:38:46.017 --> 01:38:47.952 position:16% line:83% align:start
[DOMINATOR] Colonel Wong
was utterly determined

01:38:47.986 --> 01:38:50.855 position:21% line:83% align:start
to move forward with
building Shambhala Float,

01:38:50.888 --> 01:38:53.825 position:13% line:83% align:start
even if it meant directly
disobeying his superior,

01:38:53.858 --> 01:38:54.993 position:30% line:89% align:start
Chairman Hang.

01:38:57.096 --> 01:38:59.530 position:7% line:83% align:start
[DOMINATOR] Colonel Wong knew
that the unmanned weapons

01:38:59.564 --> 01:39:02.267 position:16% line:83% align:start
provided by the Japanese
government as an incentive

01:39:02.301 --> 01:39:03.968 position:24% line:83% align:start
could be the game
changer he needed

01:39:04.002 --> 01:39:06.704 position:5% line:89% align:start
to gain control of all of SEAUn.

01:39:08.073 --> 01:39:09.040 position:33% line:83% align:start
[DOMINATOR]
At the same time,

01:39:09.074 --> 01:39:11.976 position:19% line:83% align:start
the idea of setting up
a model city overseas

01:39:12.010 --> 01:39:15.613 position:5% line:83% align:start
that would use the Sibyl System,
was very appealing to us.

01:39:16.848 --> 01:39:18.150 position:33% line:83% align:start
[DOMINATOR]
So then, it worked out

01:39:18.183 --> 01:39:20.219 position:21% line:83% align:start
that what both sides
ultimately required

01:39:20.252 --> 01:39:21.286 position:16% line:89% align:start
was an amenable chairman

01:39:21.320 --> 01:39:24.289 position:13% line:83% align:start
who would give the project
his stamp of approval.

01:39:26.291 --> 01:39:29.794 position:10% line:83% align:start
[AKANE] You intervened in a
country's domestic affairs.

01:39:29.827 --> 01:39:31.796 position:16% line:83% align:start
And worse, you conspired
with a traitor

01:39:31.829 --> 01:39:33.765 position:10% line:89% align:start
to assassinate their leader.

01:39:34.832 --> 01:39:37.236 position:19% line:83% align:start
[AKANE] That's clearly
an international crime!

01:39:38.203 --> 01:39:40.038 position:33% line:83% align:start
[DOMINATOR]
Strictly speaking.

01:39:40.072 --> 01:39:42.840 position:19% line:83% align:start
There is no such thing
as "domestic affairs"

01:39:42.874 --> 01:39:45.277 position:16% line:89% align:start
in this country anymore.

01:39:45.310 --> 01:39:48.046 position:10% line:89% align:start
Corruption, discrimination,

01:39:48.080 --> 01:39:50.715 position:21% line:83% align:start
religious and racial
confrontations.

01:39:51.716 --> 01:39:53.584 position:33% line:83% align:start
[DOMINATOR]
As of two years ago,

01:39:53.618 --> 01:39:58.123 position:7% line:83% align:start
SEAUn ceased to be recognized
as a federal nation.

01:39:58.157 --> 01:40:01.993 position:10% line:83% align:start
[AKANE] All you cared about
was expanding Sibyl's control!

01:40:02.026 --> 01:40:04.829 position:10% line:83% align:start
[DOMINATOR] Mundane desires
such as seizing territory

01:40:04.862 --> 01:40:07.132 position:16% line:89% align:start
do not exist within us.

01:40:07.166 --> 01:40:11.035 position:10% line:83% align:start
"The greatest happiness for
the greatest amount of people."

01:40:11.070 --> 01:40:16.241 position:5% line:83% align:start
In the end, it depends entirely
on how you define "greatest."

01:40:16.275 --> 01:40:20.011 position:24% line:83% align:start
You claim that our
endeavor here, is a crime.

01:40:20.044 --> 01:40:23.948 position:19% line:83% align:start
However, a crime is a
deviation from the law.

01:40:25.016 --> 01:40:27.785 position:13% line:83% align:start
[AKANE] The law isn't just
some guiding principle.

01:40:27.819 --> 01:40:28.853 position:19% line:89% align:start
It can't be sustained

01:40:28.886 --> 01:40:31.923 position:16% line:83% align:start
without the full support
and consent of the people.

01:40:31.956 --> 01:40:35.260 position:10% line:83% align:start
You never even tried to get
the approval of the citizens,

01:40:35.294 --> 01:40:38.330 position:16% line:83% align:start
when you swooped in and
started governing this place.

01:40:38.363 --> 01:40:40.132 position:27% line:83% align:start
No, all you did
was con a dictator

01:40:40.165 --> 01:40:41.766 position:16% line:89% align:start
into doing your bidding.

01:40:42.767 --> 01:40:45.270 position:16% line:83% align:start
[DOMINATOR] These people
had only two choices:

01:40:45.304 --> 01:40:47.905 position:5% line:89% align:start
Starve to death or be massacred.

01:40:47.939 --> 01:40:50.775 position:10% line:83% align:start
So we needed to take action
as swiftly as possible

01:40:50.808 --> 01:40:54.346 position:16% line:83% align:start
in order to provide them
with peace and refuge.

01:40:54.379 --> 01:40:55.880 position:19% line:89% align:start
All that we did here,

01:40:55.913 --> 01:40:58.850 position:21% line:83% align:start
was choose the most
effective solution for them.

01:41:01.286 --> 01:41:04.156 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AKANE]
Chairman Hang. Step down.

01:41:05.157 --> 01:41:07.092 position:7% line:89% align:start
Hold a free and fair election

01:41:07.126 --> 01:41:09.827 position:24% line:83% align:start
to let the people
choose a new leader

01:41:09.861 --> 01:41:12.231 position:24% line:83% align:start
and whether or not
to use the Sibyl System.

01:41:12.264 --> 01:41:15.367 position:16% line:83% align:start
That decision should be
theirs, and theirs alone.

01:41:15.400 --> 01:41:19.304 position:5% line:83% align:start
[DOMINATOR] You honestly believe
these people would reject us?

01:41:20.372 --> 01:41:21.839 position:33% line:83% align:start
[DOMINATOR]
That they would ever abandon

01:41:21.873 --> 01:41:24.775 position:27% line:83% align:start
the security of
this utopian city

01:41:24.809 --> 01:41:27.912 position:16% line:83% align:start
after actually grasping
it in their hands?

01:41:29.847 --> 01:41:32.984 position:19% line:83% align:start
[AKANE] The balancing
of freedom and security

01:41:33.017 --> 01:41:36.088 position:10% line:83% align:start
is something that they have
to determine for themselves.

01:41:37.089 --> 01:41:39.757 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AKANE]
So that they can embrace the law

